name: Butterfly Sheer Tights
description:
A flutter of butterflies make their way up your leg on ultra sheer off black stockings. The butterfly flutter measures 8.5 inches and starts above the ankle and rises to below the knee. Each butterfly ranges from. 3 inches to 1.25 inches and they are velvet textured. The pattern is only on one leg for interest. 

Each of these pantyhose are made right here in our shop. They are full length and they rise all the way to your waist. 

We have two sizes the S/M fits people who are less than 160 lbs and/or shorter than 5.6"
Our M/L fits people who are greater than 160" lbs and/or taller than 5'6" You will be asked to select your size at check out.

name: Crystal  Anatomical Heart Necklace
description:
Our anatomical heart measures approximately 1 inch in height and 3/4 inches in width. It is made from lead free safe pewter and it hangs from an elegant DNA twist silver plated chain and accompanied by a swarovski wire wrapped garnet crystal chain. This is a stunning piece that can be worn in both formal and informal settings. The heart pulls the sterling silver chain down while the crystal hangs in more of a circular fashion. It is truly beautiful on. It is finished off with a toggle clasp.

It is packaged in a kraft box with the anatomology logo and a small blank card with our heart and butterfly artwork on it.

name: Skeleton Embrace Collar
description: This is our skeletal embrace collar. It is made of lead free safe pewter, which can be bent to fit each individual comfortably. With proper placement, the fingers come together in a heart shape. However, others may prefer to wear the collar hanging lower with the fingers not coming so close together. This is a truly amazing piece that is like no other. The back of the necklace includes the striking scapula!

name: Body Necklace by Anatomology
description:
Full 3 dimensional Ribcage in the front Spine in the back! This is just an incredible piece with the back being just as spectacular as the front. A full body necklace that features the rib cage in front with the spine in the back! 

*The rib cage is made of lead free safe pewter and measures1.5 inches in length by 1 inch in width

*The spine also is made of lead free safe pewter and measures approx. 2.5 inches tall and .25 inches in width. 

*Two swarvoski garnet crystals are placed above and below the spine to give it even more impact. The chain is rhodium plated steel. 

This may need a custom fit, so when ordering please write it you consider your self to be small, medium or large. 

This item is packaged in our signature kraft anatomology box.

name: Rib Cuff Bracelet
description:
Damn this rocks. Our new rib cuff bracelet has got to be one of the coolest products we have made. It features our anatomology logo - the organic ribs as a cuff bracelet. The sides are about 5 inches in length while the middle sternum is about 3 inches. It is made to be tight around the forearm, not the wrist so that it can be comfortable. It is made of lead free safe pewter and can be bent to make your perfect fit. A truly awesome piece!

Worn by Pauley on NCIS Season Premiere 2012
